name: Never Lost in California
description:
This is an original scan from the first roll of 35mm film I ever shot. Unfortunately, the negatives from my first roll were destroyed, and only a few photographs have survived the pace of life. This photograph here always reminds me of evenings where I thought I was lost, but california made sure I wasn't. Just keep on dreaming, keep on living! 

Original photograph dimensions: 2723 × 4084 px.
